{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/3225", "repo": "rails", "body": "Hi!\r\n\r\nYup, there's certainly potential for more tidying. :-)\r\n\r\nI would like to avoid too many rake re-invocations though - at the moment I'm able to get all my assets compiled in one invocation (I don't need the undigested assets) with:\r\n\r\n```\r\nrake assets:precompile:primary RAILS_ENV=production RAILS_GROUPS=assets\r\n```\r\n\r\nIMO, we should be shooting for as few invocations of rake as possible as it just slows things down otherwise. \r\n", "_id": {"$oid": "52383942bd3543c1510100a0"}, "issue_id": 3225, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2308214", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/3225#issuecomment-2308214", "updated_at": "2011-10-06T09:53:34Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mjtko/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mjtko/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mjtko/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mjtko/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/mjtko", "login": "mjtko", "gravatar_id": "be9f8a7e49b430ac89efe1bc8aa1026d", "html_url": "https://github.com/mjtko", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mjtko/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mjtko/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mjtko/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/be9f8a7e49b430ac89efe1bc8aa1026d?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F88d16337f620f14a9d05a6b5d459802c.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mjtko/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 206834, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mjtko/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2011-10-06T09:53:34Z", "id": 2308214, "owner": "rails"}
